# =============================================================================
# Kang Open Banking — CODEOWNERS
# =============================================================================
# Enforces Guardian Standing Orders by routing reviews of high-risk surfaces
# (OpenAPI spec, DB migrations, edge functions, governance docs, ratchet
# scripts) to the API Guardians group.
#
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones for matched files.
# Replace @kang-fintech/api-guardians with the actual GitHub team handle
# once the org/team is provisioned.
# =============================================================================

# ---- 1. Default fallback -----------------------------------------------------
# Every PR gets at least one Guardian review.
*                                       @kang-fintech/api-guardians

# ---- 2. OpenAPI specification (Standing Order 1, 2, 6) -----------------------
# Any rename, removal, or version bump must be approved by Guardians.
/public/openapi.json                    @kang-fintech/api-guardians @kang-fintech/spec-architects
/public/openapi.yaml                    @kang-fintech/api-guardians @kang-fintech/spec-architects
/public/openapi-sandbox.json            @kang-fintech/api-guardians @kang-fintech/spec-architects
/public/openapi-sandbox.yaml            @kang-fintech/api-guardians @kang-fintech/spec-architects
/public/apis.json                       @kang-fintech/api-guardians
/public/apis-sandbox.json               @kang-fintech/api-guardians

# ---- 3. Quality-gate ratchets (Standing Order 2) -----------------------------
